description: Assembly Election Results 2022 LIVE Updates: Yogi Adityanath is set to meet Prime Minister Narendra Modi, Union Home Minister Amit Shah, BJP president JP Nadda, and other officials of the saffron party in Delhi today, to discuss details of UP's new cabinet, the selection of deputy chief ministers, and the swearing-in ceremony. According to reports, the BJP will want the cabinet to be 'balanced' in terms of caste, regional influence and qualifications. Keshav Prasad Maurya, Baby Rani Maurya and Brijesh Pathak are in the list of probables being considered for the post of Deputy CM.
